title: Madame And Her Niece, Madame Und Ihre Nichte

sources.title: Madame And Her Niece Madame Und Ihre Nichte
sources.description: Another German sex comedy but with Edwige Fenech. Very busy girl, Ms Fenech, with about 80 movies listed at IMDb.   At any rate, no subs for this one. The only ones I could find were for a 77 minute version of the movie which is about 5 minutes shorter than this one.
